- cs.LT (Automata and Formal Languages) is relevant as the paper deals with verification of infinite-state systems. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is possible as the paper discusses practical deductive verification. 
- cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is less likely but still possible as the paper deals with complex properties such as liveness and fairness properties.
